      "message": "[warning] Line 334: getCallIdForConversationUid() is called without the exception guard used in updateCallControlLeds(). If the tracked conversation/account is already gone during call teardown, this can throw from a call-ended signal handler and prevent the rest of onCallEnded() from running. Reuse the guarded lookup pattern here before clearing the device state.",
