      "writtenOn": "2026-06-29T17:45:17Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "[warning] Line 117: The descriptor parser only records explicit Usage items and ignores Usage Minimum/Usage Maximum ranges. HID button and LED fields commonly use ranges, so supported devices may be opened but their hook/mute inputs or LEDs will not be discovered. Add handling for local Usage Minimum/Maximum and expand those usages before consumeMain().",
      "revId": "2297172e3c04549bb267b9f8e699f8840dd15630",
      "serverId": "1e26b4c1-6b8c-47ff-9df7-501b633d3b5a"
