      "writtenOn": "2026-06-29T17:45:17Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "[error] Line 376: applyLeds() writes each LED as a separate report, but writeLed() builds a zero-filled report containing only the single requested bit. When multiple LED usages share the same output report, the later writes clear bits set by earlier writes, e.g. ringing_ can be cleared immediately by the off-hook write. Build one report per reportId containing all LED bits, then write it once.",
      "revId": "2297172e3c04549bb267b9f8e699f8840dd15630",
      "serverId": "1e26b4c1-6b8c-47ff-9df7-501b633d3b5a"
    },
